Bryan Cranston as Walter white is the bad - assertive ''good guy'' who finds himself in a lot of trouble...because of a troubled student he used to teach high school chemistry to.

Aaron Paul as Jesse Pinkman is the bad - troubled kid who narrowly escapes doing time for cooking Crystal. And guess who's brother in law is a top DEA agent and happens to be at the scene...Walter.

Walter and Jesse undertake a dangerous journey , playing the dangerous game, with dangerous people. This is a fantastic show with secrets COOKING until boiling point and the consequences spread like a cancer for Walter.